## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

**Can I get 100% financing?**
Most lenders require at least a 10% to 20% deposit. This "skin in the game" shows commitment. However, in some cases, we can find structures that require very low upfront cash.

**What if my CCRIS isn't perfect?**
Don't worry. We understand that business has ups and downs. As long as your current cash flow is healthy and you have a clear plan for the equipment, we can usually find a solution.

**Is there a penalty for early settlement?**
This depends on the specific contract. We always encourage our clients to check this. We believe in transparency—no hidden fees, no surprises.

**Does capital equipment financing cover used machinery?**
Yes, but most lenders have an age limit (usually the machine shouldn't be more than 10-15 years old at the end of the loan tenure).

